Someone gave me this on the procmail list:

SUBJECT=`formail -zxSubject:`
:0
* ^Subject:.*-Reply
{
	SUBJECT=`echo "$SUBJECT" |
	perl -p -e 's/^((Re:\s*)*)?(.*)/Re: \3/i; s/(\s*-reply)*$//i'`

	:0fhw
	|formail -i"Subject: $SUBJECT"
}

That takes care of it nicely ;-)


TjL



